OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be partly cloudy with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, heavy at first. Then the rest
OL,8,Fof the night will see variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud and some showery rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FQuite cloudy in the morning
OL,12,Fwith a scattering of showers. Becoming
OL,13,Fdrier with increasingly bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells developing through the
OL,15,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
